*Stanje* je bilo izuzetno tesko (The situation was extremely difficult).

Nadamo se da ce nas *stanje* bolje da se popravi (We hope that our situation will improve).

*Stanju* nema naznaka poboljsanja (There is no sign of improvement in the situation).

Ne znam kako da popravim *stanje* (I don't know how to improve the situation).

Ne zelim da budem u takvom *stanju* (I don't want to be in such a situation).